Introduction

HISTORY (Korean: 히스토리; Japanese: 歴史) was a five-member boy group formed by FAVE Entertainment. They made their official debut in April 26th, 2013 with the digital single "Dreamer." After four years of promotion, the group eventually disbanded in May 12, 2017.
